Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近第幾代繼承名號的歌舞伎演員的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼衛門先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再努力想想吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歌舞伎演員的側室之子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢  畢竟老師個性也挺奇特的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是稍有差錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定老師就變成歌舞伎演員了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後  這個是戒澙魁吏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是小姬媽媽的爸爸的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的外公是個很厲害的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不忌諱的講  小姬也是藝術家的血統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歌舞伎演員和日本畫的大師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:08.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師的婚姻會被反對  比起是因為漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:13.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更像是被水火不容的藝術家之間的爭執所牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  你的父親與我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是同父異母的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸有妹妹這件事還是第一次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,受打擊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,知道我和爸爸是真正的父女  安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你還那樣想過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.29,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\bord2\c&HF8F6F8&\3c&H6159B9&\pos(904,544)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為爸爸  過於溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個事件因為有涉及個人信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請全部通過律師進行確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是那一天和後藤先生一起工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frx26\fry6\frz331.8\c&H9588C3&\org(918.4,324.8)\pos(705.6,348.8)}周刊文潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\org(859.2,566.4)\frx18\fry6\frz330.9\pos(486.4,540.8)\c&HBA8F80&}記者  千田奈留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frx18\fry4\frz330.6\pos(296,651.2)\c&H867BBD&\org(670.4,673.6)}有限公司  文潮社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  你在調查那次事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請安心  我不會寫成新聞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼記者小姐會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我個人感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:12.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哪怕一點點也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是能成為改變現狀的契機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然公司那邊閉口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但那並不是後藤先生的失誤造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.59,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}周刊少年Jumpo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好壯觀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這些全部都是Jumpo嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然都在說出版不景氣  但還能賣出這麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,趕緊收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,餵誰快叫下救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生？ 後藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個貨架會失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因為有人為了看書而偷偷抽去了幾冊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要儘快地洩露在網上逞英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然公司有嚴令禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然  不是後藤先生幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生說過自己討厭漫畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是這間病房的患者吧  我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  已經過了一年了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是諷刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明逃離了漫畫  結果卻被漫畫所壓倒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交了厄運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是不是Jumpo  而是Saturday或者漫畫人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不會堆高到能砸到人的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:58.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個時候  他似乎輾轉在不習慣的體力勞動之間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:03.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生活貧困潦倒  都到了必須得賣掉房子的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,存款的話應該有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,基本上都花掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了搜尋妻子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz350.4\pos(160,73.6)\3c&H30323F&}8人失蹤。持續搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz351.9\pos(1017.6,224)\3c&H2D303D&}事故現場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\fad(1100,0)\c&H0F0E10&\3c&H646464&\frx6\fry354\pos(582.8,876.8)\org(600.4,780.8)\frz255}原因調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在小姬出生後不久發生的海難事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子一直下落不明  即便搜索行動結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他也自己雇了專業人員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直堅信著她還活著  繼續搜索下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,邊畫著漫畫持續了十年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後在小姬上初中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道是從哪兒走漏了風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師他在盼望妻子回來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被周刊雜誌當作是美談而大肆報道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frx6\fry0\frz285.5\move(1122,444,1204,434,0,5402)}有名的漫畫家G氏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H403D3E&\frx4\fry358\frz22.59\move(2,274,10,300,0,5402)}時至今日依然在等著妻子回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&H615D60&\frz24.82\frx24\fry354\move(584,256,666,258,0,5402)}獨占新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&H4A4848&\3c&HC7C5C6&\frx8\fry356\frz25.6\move(208,960,286,964,0,5402)}作品的背後被隱藏的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\pos(254,730)\frx8\fry356\frz23.69}妻子都死了還在畫著雞〇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\frx10\fry358\frz24.74\pos(414,960)}真的無語了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\frz334.4\org(1398,596)\pos(360,550)\frx4\fry0}在這種時候  雞雞復雞雞（）什麼的也太不走心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4B4A4A&\frx6\fry4\pos(380,572)\org(1036,604)\frz334}當時不還是黃段子的全盛期麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\c&H4B4A4A&\frx4\fry0\frz331.3\pos(-10,986)\org(1028,1032)}作為一個人來說已經完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.86,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這傢伙畫的漫畫已經讓人笑不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是不管畫什麼都無法使人發笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師他封筆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  「風之緊身褲」還是好好地完結了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最終回還挺不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:10.51,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&HEFECEE&\frx358\fry10\move(449.2,603.6,452,-450)}全國高中生美術展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,結果雖然失去了收入和工作  非常的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但還是把小姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一路順利地送入了高中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是諷刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:18.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  似乎是好好繼承了外公那邊的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.18,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\frz270\pos(666,300)\c&H5C5A51&}高中三年級  後藤姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.18,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\fs50\c&H304C70&\frz270.6\pos(1248,380)}大臣獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做漫畫家的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辭職了以後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸在我的面前一直都是笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的太過溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我媽媽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他一直都非常關心你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說  把這兒的鑰匙給我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把這個交給姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果我出了什麼事  用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:49.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把房裡的東西都賣了  用來供養那孩子的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這麼說來好奇怪  屋內並沒有變空哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然本人有點難以啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該是我媽媽想讓你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸的工作成果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.57,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}隱瞞之事  有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作畫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師他？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然我是怕姐姐會哭才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過似乎沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老師  還有各位？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這種地方竟然有帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  你爸爸恢復意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是好消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  壞消息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:17.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是…誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太俗套了吧  記憶喪失啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便是漫畫這樣的分鏡草稿也過不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院先生  這兒是病房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師他才復活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又沒去世好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您忘記小姬了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會忘記姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬還只有十歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是記憶停留在女兒十歲的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近七年間的記憶似乎不翼而飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼  會是七年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如說有什麼印象很深的事情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,記憶障礙裡挺常有的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,七年前嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬十歲的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有什麼那麼印象深刻的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道不是最開心的時期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作也好  私人生活也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是我擔任責編的時期呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.88,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6E4A3B&\pos(577.6,633.6)}後藤可久士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不好好進行康復訓練恢復肌肉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:40.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他試圖逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓我見見姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請稍微冷靜一點後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  我能夠理解你想見姬的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但姬見到你現在的這個樣子她會擔心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,絕對不能讓她看到我這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對的  對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你先等到康復訓練完後也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在您也只有手指能夠隨意動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,手指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少為了讀者  我也得繼續畫緊身褲的後續了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個連載啊  早在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了圓滿完結是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他好像以為漫畫還在連載
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,該把真相講出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這會讓他很受打擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像這樣我們這幾個人聚在一起幹活不知道是多久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒想到我又再次拿起了筆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是爸爸的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是新來的助手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我現在走不開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思啊  我能拜託你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心我的女兒姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,直到幫忙做家務的納德拉小姐來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心她獨自在家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以你能幫我照看一下她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,之前我也拜託過十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一點用都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:38.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,離姬回家前還有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這之前你慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這之前還有我能夠幫忙做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:57.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能問你件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:22.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬你真的沒有注意到你爸爸的隱瞞之事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就這麼一無所知  沉浸在父親的溺愛之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父親他一定很喜歡畫漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到父親他工作的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十分的認真  看上去特別的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,與其重新回想起來再次讓父親失去漫畫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如就這樣更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸就會一直把你給忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  你覺得這樣就好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果小姬你覺得這樣就好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  你爸爸情況變好了可要給我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目黑川偵探事務所隨時接收委託
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是  要是能夠有我幫忙的事情我都會幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟小姬你是我的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓你獨自一人  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給  十丸院  這週的連載
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您還在繼續畫著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然還真是7年前的後續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這一話上的內容基本上和以前畫的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,照這個樣子  每週完成原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,七年過後說不定就想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的不能夠說出真相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都說了會適得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得讓他自己回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們沒事的  為了老師我們會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少你們放過小羅砂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,196.8)\frz20.13}周刊少年漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto in 7 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HC56B63&\3c&H5A556F&\frz298.4\pos(1188.8,366)}塗黑女僕的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs40\frz313.9\c&H1C00BE&\b1\pos(793.6,617.6)}大人氣感謝！\N\h\h\h{\fs55\c&HE9E9E9&\3c&H2708B0&\b1}刊頭彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在她可是我們的招牌作家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你暫且先幫我把下回給停載了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然老師他很喜歡漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫漫畫的時候看上去最為開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很久沒有看到過那樣的老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對於老師而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓他畫漫畫就是對他最好的康復訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:48.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:49.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,關於下回故事情節的討論
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不帶上我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都挺為老師您著想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都是很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:07.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您畫漫畫的時候  看上去特別幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:20.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您一直以來都隱瞞著自己最愛的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最後不得不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我卻沒能夠注意到這些  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哪怕一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要能夠繼續畫漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:41.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對於老師您來說  這就是最大的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我最大的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和最令我高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是希望姬能夠健康長大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有事想拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有件東西無論如何也想讓我爸爸看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:31.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我  果然是個任性得無可救藥的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我果然還是覺得  和爸爸你在一起最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  突然把你們叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是見外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目黑川偵探事務所  接下了時隔許久的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家要鼓足幹勁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frx14\fry26\c&HC8B8A1&\1a&H20&\pos(910.4,56)\org(419.2,-91.2)\frz307.5}江之島電鐵線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord3\frx14\fry26\c&HE8E1E9&\1a&H20&\frz310.9\3c&HA3C45A&\pos(840,393.6)\org(396.8,302.4)}七里之濱站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼老師  我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天我們再來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這些箱子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.88,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz326.7\frx22\fry20\pos(1352,424)\org(1665.6,401.6)\b1}風之緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是鎌倉家裡的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請看一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:06.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不記得我有畫過這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不枉我們奮戰到了最後  這回的故事真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那老師  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  確實收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:40.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提  上週的調查問卷也挺普通的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  對不起  我擦得太用力了給原稿弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:48.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  今天工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  感覺這回的故事的收尾有些差強人意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個段子上次好像用過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想到了個超級有趣的段子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,高爾夫俱樂部其實就是蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天的老師認真得猶如鬼神附體一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簡直就是漫畫之鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,邪靈退散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你們單純就是想讓我扮鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸來扮鬼  你可以扔在爸爸身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,扔在爸爸身上  我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看鏡頭  笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說些什麼啊  這可是一生一次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我成為中學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從今天起  這裡就是我們倆的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是稍微有些破舊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:35.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要和爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管是哪裡都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:42.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今後也請你多多關照  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我十八歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:58.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:00.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
